<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>Sreek’s Blog</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />

    <style>
      /* -----------------------------
         Gwern-style minimal system
      ------------------------------ */

      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 3rem 1.2rem;
        max-width: 820px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
        font-family: serif;
        background: #fafafa;
        color: #111;
        line-height: 1.55;
      }
      div { 
        padding: 1rem 1.2rem;
      }

      a {
        color: #000;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }

      /* header */
      .meta {
        font-family: monospace;
        font-size: 11px;
        opacity: 0.6;
        letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 2.6rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin: 0.5rem 0;
      }

      .subtitle {
        font-style: italic;
        opacity: 0.7;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
      }

      /* nav */
      nav {
        font-family: monospace;
        font-size: 12px;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
      }

      nav span {
        opacity: 0.5;
      }

      /* post block */
      article {
        padding: 2rem 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
      }

      .post-meta {
        font-family: monospace;
        font-size: 11px;
        opacity: 0.5;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        display: flex;
        gap: 0.8rem;
      }

      h2 {
        font-size: 1.4rem;
        margin: 0.3rem 0 0.7rem;
      }

      .excerpt {
        font-style: italic;
        opacity: 0.75;
        max-width: 65ch;
      }

      .expand {
        font-family: monospace;
        font-size: 11px;
        margin-top: 0.8rem;
      }

      /* side note */
      aside {
        margin-top: 4rem;
        padding-left: 1rem;
        border-left: 2px solid #ddd;
        font-style: italic;
        opacity: 0.8;
      }

      footer {
        margin-top: 4rem;
        font-family: monospace;
        font-size: 10px;
        opacity: 0.5;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
        padding-top: 1rem;
      }

      @media (max-width: 600px) {
        h1 {
          font-size: 2rem;
        }

        footer {
          flex-direction: column;
          gap: 0.5rem;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body> 
    <h1>Archives</h1>
    <div class="meta">An Archive of various unrelated posts and data</div>
    <main> 
        <div> <a href = "/math">Math:</a> Various math related posts and excercises mostly about differential equations
        </div>
        <div> <a href = "/archives/email_fix">Email Archive of "Perry HS Guitar club incident in hamilton high school":</a> An incedent where cross-school communication was accidentaly enabled and students were ushered temporarily to an age of information transfer</div>
        <div> <a href = "/book_reviews">Book Reviews:</a> Supposed to be book reviews of various books not implemented robustly, incomplete, and abondoned for now.
        </div>
    </main>


    </body>